# Component Structure

Pablo uses a component-based architecture with Svelte 5. The components are organized as follows:

## Artboard Components
The artboard is the main canvas where designs are rendered:

- [src/lib/components/artboard/Artboard.svelte](mdc:src/lib/components/artboard/Artboard.svelte) - Main artboard component
- [src/lib/components/HtmlRenderer.svelte](mdc:src/lib/components/HtmlRenderer.svelte) - Renders HTML designs

## Chat Components
The AI assistant interface for generating and modifying designs:

- [src/lib/components/chat/AssistantPanel.svelte](mdc:src/lib/components/chat/AssistantPanel.svelte) - Panel containing the chat interface
- [src/lib/components/chat/VisionChat.svelte](mdc:src/lib/components/chat/VisionChat.svelte) - AI chat interface that can analyze designs

## UI Components
Pablo uses shadcn-svelte UI components organized in the `src/lib/components/ui` directory:

- `src/lib/components/ui/button` - Button components
- `src/lib/components/ui/card` - Card components
- `src/lib/components/ui/tabs` - Tab components
- And many other UI primitives